{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Dive into the Darkness!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Enter the captivating universe of <i>Monochrome Nemesis</i>,</strong> a die and retry game in black and white pixel art, offering a retro black and white experience. Relentlessly face a formidable knight who gains strength and strategy with each duel. Each victory makes your Nemesis more powerful, ensuring a constant and renewed challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478450/extras/nemesis.png?t=1739003680\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>For Challenge Seekers</strong>, <i>Monochrome Nemesis</i> is designed for those who seek a true challenge. Each combat demands skill and perseverance, putting your abilities to the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A Game Without Limits, Except Yours</strong>. <i>Monochrome Nemesis</i> is a record game, with no mechanical limits other than your own endurance. How far will you go to defeat your Nemesis?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Prepare to take on the ultimate challenge and prove your worth against your Nemesis.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Created with Godot by an Independent Developer.</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478450/extras/frog_run.gif?t=1739003680\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to the hell !","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3478450/dfafb127baadae5d5fb1a6de56b404cb2d21dfe8.jpg"},{"name":"YEEAH !","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamsta